content.title: Action Items
content.visibleText:
Create a user profile object that stores information such as user preferences and job responsibilities.
Define an object schema for user profiles that will load one object per user, with no UI initially.
Store user profile data in XO or DynamoDB, but avoid setting up DynamoDB just for this purpose.
Add a schema for audio transcripts and decide whether to continue with Pinecone for simplicity.
Expand the indexing to include all TPOs and set the history to 14 days.
Propose a solution for adding audio transcripts.

content.visibleText: Settings panel What would you like AI Assist to know about you? I am an AI Engineer working primarily on AI-based applications I like long and detailed very explanatory answers. When I ask a question that requires search, I generally prefer deep search that generates very detailed answers I am proficient in Typescript and Python but sometimes a bit more of Typescript than python, so if I ever ask for an explanation of python code, ensure to include analogies to typescript to help me understand faster At a minimum, should be your bio and maybe details about your team, department or areas of responsibility How would you like AI Assist to respond? I want all responses to be in Nigerian Pidgin English Language, casual and use emojis. ALWAYS use Emojis!! Still keep all the facts and maintain accuracy and high quality responses.
